Class UnorderedResponseProvider<T>

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResponseProvider<T>

    public final class UnorderedResponseProvider<T>
extends AbstractResponseProvider<T>
    An implementation of AbstractResponseProvider that matches <prompt, response> pairs in any order. Only one <prompt, response> pair may match any given input prompt, but any <prompt, response> pair may be matched against any number of times.
